		position: absolute;
		right: 5px;
		top: 0;
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		cursor: pointer;
		display: none;
	}
	
	#tbl > tr:hover > td > span {
		display: inline;
	}
</style>
</head>
<body>
	<h1>자료실(탐색기) wevapp > files</h1>
	<table id="tbl">
		<tr>
			<th>파일명</th>
			<th>크기</th>
			<th>수정된 날짜</th>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td id="a">
				<% for (File file : tbl) { %>
					<div style="background-image:url(pic/<%= file.getName() %>);" data-modal-button="view" data-filename="<%= file.getName() %>">
					<span title="delete" onclick="del('<%= file.getName() %>');">&times;</span>
					</div>
				<% } %>
			</td>
		</tr>
	</table>
	
